{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-23","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 23","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Element <code>li</code> se koristi za kreiranje stavke liste u uređenoj ili neuređenoj listi.</p>\n<p>Evo primera stavki liste u neuređenoj listi:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;ul>\n  &#x3C;li>milk&#x3C;/li>\n  &#x3C;li>cheese&#x3C;/li>\n&#x3C;/ul>\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar <code>ul</code> elementa, ugnjezdi tri stavke liste koje prikazuju tri omiljene stvari mačke:</p>\n<p><code>catnip</code></p>\n<p><code>laser pointers</code></p>\n<p><code>lasagna</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5dfb5ecbeacea3f48c6300b1","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"basic-html","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-23"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          \n        </ul>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[14,16],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da imaš tri <code>li</code> elementa. Svaki <code>li</code> element treba da ima svoju početnu i završnu oznaku.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('li'), 3);\nassert.lengthOf(code.match(/<\\/li\\>/g), 3);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš tri elementa sa tekstom <code>li</code>, <code>catnip</code>, <code>laser pointers</code> i <code>lasagna</code> u bilo kom redosledu. Možda si propustio neki tekst ili imaš greške u kucanju.</p>","testString":"assert.deepStrictEqual(\n  [...document.querySelectorAll('li')]\n    .map((item) => item.innerText?.trim().replace(/\\s+/g, ' ').toLowerCase())\n    .sort((a, b) => a.localeCompare(b)),\n  ['catnip', 'lasagna', 'laser pointers']\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tri <code>li</code> elementa treba da budu postavljena između početne i završne oznake <code>ul</code> elementa.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(\n  [...document.querySelectorAll('li')].filter(\n    (item) => item.parentNode.nodeName === 'UL'\n  ), 3\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/basic-html/#workshop-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-23","certification":"basic-html","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"basic-html","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-24","prevChallengePath":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-22","id":"5dfb5ecbeacea3f48c6300b1","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-23"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}